'''Kevin Hanssen''', ni [[Zimbabwe|umukinnyi wa firime Zimbabwe]], umwanditsi akaba n'umucuranzi<ref>https://tantor.com/narrator/kevin-hanssen.html</ref>.  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''Mind Games'', ''Mugabe'' na ''The Telling Room''<ref>https://www.musixmatch.com/es/letras/Kevin-Hanssen/Wings-To-Fly</ref> . 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1994, yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts muri UNISA, [[Afurika y'Epfo]]<ref>https://kevinhanssen.com/</ref>.  Ni n'umunyamuryango washinze Over The Edge Theatre Company<ref>https://www.ussportscamps.com/coaches/kevin-hanssen</ref>.  Yakinnye mu ikinamico 'A Man Like You' yakinwe mu makinamico menshi ya [[Zimbabwe]]<ref>https://www.musixmatch.com/es/letras/Kevin-Hanssen/Wings-To-Fly</ref>. 

== Ibihembo<ref>https://newsofafrica.org/zimbabwe-multi-award-winning-local-feature-film-mind-games-finally-premiered-at-sterkinekor-eastgate-harare.html</ref> ==
Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mu minsi mikuru mpuzamahanga. 

* BAT Umukinnyi mwiza ushyigikira - ''Ntabwo ndi Rappaport'' (1993)
* Tora igihembo cya Fringe, Iserukiramuco rya Edinburgh - ''Ijoro rya cumi na kabiri'' (2001)
* Umwuka wa Fringe Igihembo, Iserukiramuco rya Edinburgh - ''Yavutse Afurika'' (2003)
* BAT Igihembo Cyabakinnyi Cyiza - ''Miss Julie'' (2010)
* AFDIS Igihembo Cyabakinnyi Cyiza - ''Umugenzuzi Hamagara'' (2015)
